00:14:51,427 --> 00:14:55,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Here it comes !
His entry speed's just incredible !</font></font>

172
00:15:05,727 --> 00:15:07,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What the hell are you doing, Bunta ?!</font>

173
00:15:08,107 --> 00:15:09,947
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I need a smoke.</font>

174
00:15:09,947 --> 00:15:13,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I...I...In the middle of drifting ?!</font>

175
00:15:19,927 --> 00:15:20,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Oh, no !</font></font>

176
00:15:25,357 --> 00:15:28,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Oh well, good enough.</font>

177
00:15:31,097 --> 00:15:33,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Now, I'd better get serious.</font>

178
00:15:34,627 --> 00:15:38,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You really haven't changed since the old days !</font>

179
00:15:38,987 --> 00:15:42,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Let me get out !</font>

180
00:15:58,857 --> 00:16:02,757
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Oh man, what a terrible night.</font></font>

181
00:16:02,757 --> 00:16:06,287
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">They say you don't feel fear 
when a skilled driver goes fast, but...</font></font>

182
00:16:07,017 --> 00:16:09,137
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">That's a total lie.</font></font>

183
00:16:09,737 --> 00:16:14,047
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Bunta's super crazy when
 it comes to pursuing speed.</font></font>

184
00:16:16,977 --> 00:16:23,247
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">And even Bunta recognizes Takumi, so he must be...</font></font>

185
00:16:25,647 --> 00:16:27,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Akagi's White Comet ?</font>

186
00:16:28,307 --> 00:16:31,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">People call Takahashi Ryosuke that ?</font>

187
00:16:31,107 --> 00:16:33,737
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah. It was about three years ago...</font>

188
00:16:34,247 --> 00:16:36,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Akagi's level was already high.</font>

189
00:16:36,657 --> 00:16:42,567
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Then word spread quickly when a
super fast white FC3S showed up.</font>

190
00:16:43,087 --> 00:16:46,297
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That was the lone wolf Takahashi Ryosuke.</font>

191
00:16:46,727 --> 00:16:50,337
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The "lone wolf" ?
 What about the Akagi Red Suns ?</font>

192
00:16:50,847 --> 00:16:56,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takahashi Ryosuke formed the Red Suns later. 
The goal was to perfect driving technique.</font>

193
00:16:57,067 --> 00:17:01,757
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">They participate in gymkhana and circuit runs.</font>

194
00:17:01,757 --> 00:17:05,697
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The team's fundamentally different 
from the usual groups of friends.</font>

195
00:17:06,457 --> 00:17:09,227
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's why their level is so high.</font>

196
00:17:09,227 --> 00:17:16,957
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Together with his brother Keisuke, they're now known as the Takahashi Brothers, but to me...</font>

197
00:17:16,957 --> 00:17:20,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">...Akagi's White Comet sounds right.</font>

198
00:17:20,307 --> 00:17:25,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takahashi Ryosuke's charisma is unmatched in Gunma.</font>

199
00:17:27,647 --> 00:17:31,757
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Akagi's White Comet, huh ?
 Sounds awesome.</font>

200
00:17:31,757 --> 00:17:35,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">This Saturday's battle is getting more interesting.{, isn't it Takumi ? Right ?}</font>

201
00:17:35,107 --> 00:17:36,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Right, Takumi ?</font>

202
00:17:36,507 --> 00:17:37,467
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Isn't it ?</font>

203
00:17:39,657 --> 00:17:40,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Huh ?</font>

204
00:17:41,297 --> 00:17:43,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Where is that low tension coming from ?</font>

205
00:17:43,657 --> 00:17:46,367
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You said you were excited the other day !</font>

206
00:17:49,247 --> 00:17:52,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Are you going to be alright ?</font>

207
00:18:04,307 --> 00:18:05,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I heard this at the shop.</font>

208
00:18:05,907 --> 00:18:10,887
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Is it true that Ryosuke turned down
an offer from a professional team ?</font>

209
00:18:11,337 --> 00:18:13,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah, it's true.</font>

210
00:18:13,367 --> 00:18:14,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I see.</font>

211
00:18:14,707 --> 00:18:19,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Is it because it's hard to strike a
 balance with his med school studies ?</font>

212
00:18:19,707 --> 00:18:22,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That'd be a piece of cake for my brother.</font>

213
00:18:22,157 --> 00:18:23,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Then why ?</font>

214
00:18:23,657 --> 00:18:30,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">RS Giga is an elite team with stellar 
achievements in production car racing at Fuji.{???}</font>

215
00:18:30,257 --> 00:18:35,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Becoming a pro driver, stepping into 
the spotlight, and getting recognized...</font>

216
00:18:35,057 --> 00:18:39,027
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{hashiriya}That's the success story 
every street racer dreams of.</font>

217
00:18:39,417 --> 00:18:43,957
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Kenta, Ryosuke's not interested
 in the world of the pros.</font>

218
00:18:43,957 --> 00:18:48,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Then why is he so into
 gymkhanas and circuit runs ?</font>

219
00:18:48,657 --> 00:18:50,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What's the reason ?</font>

220
00:18:53,657 --> 00:18:55,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The public street...</font>

221
00:18:56,377 --> 00:18:59,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Process is what matters to my brother...</font>

222
00:18:59,657 --> 00:19:01,487
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">...in order to be the best on the public street.</font>

223
00:19:23,507 --> 00:19:26,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Welcome home, Brother !
 Is your FC ready ?</font>

224
00:19:26,937 --> 00:19:29,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah. I'm going to take
 it for a spin on Mt. Akagi.</font>

225
00:19:29,307 --> 00:19:30,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Are you coming ?</font>

226
00:19:31,017 --> 00:19:31,817
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll be right there !{Right away !}</font>

227
00:19:43,057 --> 00:19:45,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So, how much power did you add ?</font>

228
00:19:46,847 --> 00:19:48,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Don't be surprised, Keisuke.</font>

229
00:19:49,307 --> 00:19:52,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's got 260 hp at the maximum.</font>

230
00:19:52,407 --> 00:19:55,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You dropped it from 340 hp ?!</font>

231
00:19:55,807 --> 00:19:58,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What's the point of slowing the car down ?</font>

232
00:19:58,507 --> 00:20:01,587
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{After the battle against him,} You must've learned the lesson
 the hard way after you raced him.</font>

233
00:20:01,587 --> 00:20:05,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{kudari}Total balance is the key to
 mastering the downhill, not power.</font>

234
00:20:07,167 --> 00:20:12,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Sometimes you have to lower the power to go faster, which makes street racing complex.</font>

235
00:20:13,607 --> 00:20:18,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So Akina's Eight-Six is a formidable opponent ?</font>

236
00:20:19,387 --> 00:20:21,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You could say that.</font>

237
00:20:22,297 --> 00:20:29,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I was confident I could manage big power on the downhill, so this de-tune is humiliating.</font>

238
00:20:29,657 --> 00:20:34,847
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I have to put my pride aside in order to win.</font>

239
00:20:53,827 --> 00:20:58,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Incredible. The exit speed at 
the corners is definitely faster.</font>

240
00:20:58,697 --> 00:21:01,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">There's another reason 
why I dropped the FC's power.</font>

241
00:21:02,467 --> 00:21:06,937
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">If I just out-power the Eight-Six on
 the straightaways, that's not a victory.</font>

242
00:21:06,937 --> 00:21:09,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{sorejaa}That won't satisfy me.</font>

243
00:21:12,777 --> 00:21:14,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Technique against technique.</font>

244
00:21:17,377 --> 00:21:19,377
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Drift against drift. That's my way.</font>

245
00:21:20,287 --> 00:21:23,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{konna}I'm happy to have met a driver
 who makes me feel this way.</font>

246
00:21:24,697 --> 00:21:31,047
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I feel like I've changed back to Akagi's White Comet, instead of Takahashi Ryosuke of the Red Suns.</font>

247
00:21:31,727 --> 00:21:32,527
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Brother...</font>

248
00:21:46,867 --> 00:21:50,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takumi, aren't you happy to be with me ?</font>

249
00:21:51,977 --> 00:21:57,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You look spaced out, 
like your mind's somewhere else.</font>

250
00:21:57,707 --> 00:21:59,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I do ? Sorry.</font>

251
00:22:03,217 --> 00:22:04,327
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Thinking about cars ?</font>

252
00:22:08,857 --> 00:22:15,497
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The day after tomorrow, I'll race against a driver, who's very skilled, fast, and famous.</font>

253
00:22:16,257 --> 00:22:22,347
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{saikin}Lately, I've been thinking about
 him a lot, and feeling uneasy.</font>

254
00:22:23,417 --> 00:22:25,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Maybe this is pressure.</font>

255
00:22:27,907 --> 00:22:29,137
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Is that it ?</font>

256
00:22:29,907 --> 00:22:32,547
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Cars have to be fast ?</font>

257
00:22:34,177 --> 00:22:36,167
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">If you don't like it, just ignore it.</font>

258
00:22:37,227 --> 00:22:41,447
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Just because someone challenged
 you doesn't mean you have to take it.</font>

259
00:22:43,177 --> 00:22:46,857
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I don't hate it.
 I don't know if I can win, but...</font>

260
00:22:48,367 --> 00:22:50,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">...I have no intention of running away.</font>

261
00:22:52,747 --> 00:22:55,067
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's so you, Takumi.</font>

262
00:22:56,457 --> 00:22:59,777
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Deep down, you're really eager to race, right ?</font>

263
00:23:00,827 --> 00:23:06,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You look modest,
 but you're a very competitive type.</font>

264
00:23:07,587 --> 00:23:09,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I've known all along.</font>

265
00:23:10,257 --> 00:23:13,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I wasn't the soccer club's 
manager for no reason.</font>

266
00:23:21,697 --> 00:23:23,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Wanna head home ?</font>

267
00:23:23,007 --> 00:23:29,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Just a little longer, let's talk 
just a little bit longer in the car.</font>

268
00:23:29,807 --> 00:23:31,167
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Okay.</font>

269
00:23:35,887 --> 00:23:38,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I know one more thing.</font>

270
00:23:40,497 --> 00:23:49,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I know why you punched an older student in the soccer club's locker room.</font>

271
00:23:50,987 --> 00:23:56,827
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">A junior student told me what really 
happened long after you quit the club.</font>

272
00:23:58,607 --> 00:24:02,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Natsuki's body's just gorgeous.</font>

273
00:24:02,307 --> 00:24:03,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I can't get enough of this.</font>

274
00:24:03,307 --> 00:24:07,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Hey, I'll have dirty thoughts every
 time I see Mogi's face from now on.</font>

275
00:24:07,607 --> 00:24:08,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Don't be so envious.</font>

276
00:24:09,607 --> 00:24:10,827
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The other day...</font>

277
00:24:12,937 --> 00:24:16,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Cut your dirty talk.</font>

278
00:24:16,457 --> 00:24:18,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It gets on my nerves !</font>

279
00:24:18,557 --> 00:24:22,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What's wrong, Fujiwara ?!
 I'm dating Natsuki !</font>

280
00:24:22,007 --> 00:24:23,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll say whatever I want !</font>

281
00:24:24,027 --> 00:24:28,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Besides, how can you talk 
to senior students like that ?</font>

282
00:24:28,707 --> 00:24:31,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Like I care ?!</font>

283
00:24:35,427 --> 00:24:40,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You got angry for my sake.</font>

284
00:24:40,207 --> 00:24:43,777
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Sorry, I misunderstood you for a long time.</font>

285
00:24:44,427 --> 00:24:47,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's okay. It doesn't matter now.</font>

286
00:25:43,527 --> 00:25:46,647
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">See ?
 Something's wrong with Takumi.</font>

287
00:25:46,647 --> 00:25:48,647
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm sure of it.</font>

288
00:25:48,647 --> 00:25:50,787
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Now that you mentioned it...</font>

289
00:25:50,787 --> 00:25:54,417
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">But Takumi's always spaced out.</font>

290
00:25:54,897 --> 00:26:00,857
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He's even worse lately. 
Almost completely out of it.</font>

291
00:26:00,857 --> 00:26:05,727
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">At first, I thought he was concerned
 about tomorrow's battle, but...</font>

292
00:26:05,727 --> 00:26:07,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's not ? Then what is it ?</font>

293
00:26:08,447 --> 00:26:10,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Remember what Kenji said earlier ?</font>

294
00:26:13,067 --> 00:26:19,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You mean about how Kenji's friend
 saw a panda Trueno with a girl inside ?</font>

295
00:26:19,007 --> 00:26:22,617
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Hey, why can't Takumi have a girlfriend ?</font>

296
00:26:22,617 --> 00:26:25,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Stop. I know what's going on.</font>

297
00:26:25,257 --> 00:26:27,887
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He must be lost in love.</font>

298
00:26:28,207 --> 00:26:29,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He is ?!</font>

299
00:26:36,927 --> 00:26:38,297
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Welcome.</font>

300
00:26:39,147 --> 00:26:40,537
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">High octane, right ?</font>

301
00:26:40,537 --> 00:26:41,947
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yup. Fill it up.</font>

302
00:26:41,947 --> 00:26:43,137
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Right away.</font>

303
00:26:43,927 --> 00:26:45,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">No need to clean the glass.</font>

304
00:26:46,067 --> 00:26:47,447
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Okay. Thanks.</font>

305
00:26:48,287 --> 00:26:52,187
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Hey, being love sick the day 
before a battle is pretty bad.</font>

306
00:26:52,707 --> 00:26:54,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What should we do, Iketani ?</font>

307
00:26:56,617 --> 00:27:01,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I want romance. A passionate one.</font>

308
00:27:01,457 --> 00:27:03,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">This isn't the time for that.</font>

309
00:27:04,467 --> 00:27:05,987
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll take care of this...</font>

310
00:27:06,567 --> 00:27:12,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">...while being completely free from personal envy like
 "How come he's the only lucky one ?!"</font>

311
00:27:21,757 --> 00:27:23,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So, what's this about ?{'s the business ?}</font>

312
00:27:24,247 --> 00:27:28,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You've been seeing a girl lately, 
without telling me{ lately}, haven't you ?</font>

313
00:27:30,007 --> 00:27:32,187
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I didn't mean to keep it a secret from you.</font>

314
00:27:32,187 --> 00:27:35,187
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">But I don't have to report to you, do I ?</font>

315
00:27:35,187 --> 00:27:37,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">No excuses. 
Just answer my questions.</font>

316
00:27:37,707 --> 00:27:41,997
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So, how far have you gone ? 
Be honest.</font>

317
00:27:43,107 --> 00:27:45,567
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">How far...? 
Up to Akina Lake.</font>

318
00:27:46,157 --> 00:27:49,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You moron, that's not what I meant !</font>

319
00:27:49,457 --> 00:27:52,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Hey, watch out !
 Itsuki, watch where you're going !</font>

320
00:27:53,247 --> 00:27:57,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You must have kissed her already, I suppose.</font>

321
00:27:58,207 --> 00:27:59,187
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I did.</font>

322
00:27:59,427 --> 00:28:01,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What the hell...?!</font>

323
00:28:01,557 --> 00:28:05,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Stop that ! I mean it !</font>

324
00:28:08,647 --> 00:28:12,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takumi, you've been acting
 weird for the last few days.</font>

325
00:28:13,287 --> 00:28:16,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I've been thinking about something for a while.</font>

326
00:28:17,267 --> 00:28:21,147
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I know. It's not about
 tomorrow's battle, is it ?</font>

327
00:28:22,027 --> 00:28:27,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You're right. I've been thinking
 about what comes after that.</font>

328
00:28:27,447 --> 00:28:29,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">After that ?</font>

329
00:28:29,507 --> 00:28:36,367
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">How dare you say that to someone like me who 
hasn't had a girlfriend for 18 years and counting !</font>

330
00:28:36,367 --> 00:28:39,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">There's only one thing after a kiss.</font>

331
00:28:39,657 --> 00:28:42,447
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">A hotel, right{you know} ? A hotel !</font>

332
00:28:42,447 --> 00:28:44,347
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What are you talking about ?</font>

333
00:28:45,467 --> 00:28:49,767
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm talking about what will 
happen after tomorrow's battle.</font>

334
00:28:50,667 --> 00:28:56,447
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I don't have any concrete vision, 
so it keeps bugging me.</font>

335
00:28:56,447 --> 00:28:59,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Huh ? What're you talking about ?</font>

336
00:28:59,607 --> 00:29:02,487
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Don't you see what I mean ?</font>

337
00:29:02,487 --> 00:29:07,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">No, I don't. You think there has
 to be something after the battle ?</font>

338
00:29:07,107 --> 00:29:12,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You don't need anything. 
You're already fast enough.</font>

339
00:29:13,057 --> 00:29:14,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">No, I'm not.</font>

340
00:29:15,147 --> 00:29:17,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You are.</font>

341
00:29:17,007 --> 00:29:22,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Seriously, Takumi, please stop thinking
 about the small stuff and focus on the battle.</font>

342
00:29:22,557 --> 00:29:25,697
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">By this time tomorrow, 
you and Takahashi Ryosuke...</font>

343
00:29:28,807 --> 00:29:30,757
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">A car's climbing up.</font>

344
00:29:30,757 --> 00:29:33,047
