351
00:30:18,587 --> 00:30:20,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Have you forgotten ?</font>

352
00:30:21,507 --> 00:30:23,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You beat those two.</font>

353
00:30:24,137 --> 00:30:28,047
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">My victory was under a specific condition...</font>

354
00:30:28,977 --> 00:30:34,307
