371
00:32:43,617 --> 00:32:45,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You know boys...</font>

372
00:32:45,457 --> 00:32:47,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">They like cars.</font>

373
00:32:48,137 --> 00:32:50,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Are they that interesting ?</font>

374
00:32:50,157 --> 00:32:54,977
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Sure they are. 
You can go anywhere you like.</font>

375
00:32:55,417 --> 00:32:56,617
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Is that all ?</font>

376
00:32:57,327 --> 00:32:59,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">There's more to it.</font>

377
00:32:59,257 --> 00:33:02,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Any licensed driver can drive a car, but...</font>

378
00:33:02,857 --> 00:33:07,937
