do to become a faster driver.</font>

381
00:33:19,547 --> 00:33:23,347
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I feel good thinking about things like that.</font>

382
00:33:25,257 --> 00:33:28,227
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takumi, you're a pervert.</font>

383
00:33:29,447 --> 00:33:30,867
