389
00:33:45,017 --> 00:33:46,427
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Never mind. Never mind.</font>

390
00:33:48,507 --> 00:33:49,587
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Sheesh.</font>

391
00:33:56,217 --> 00:34:00,307
