395
00:34:14,607 --> 00:34:16,087
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{yakusoku}Promise ?</font>

396
00:35:04,257 --> 00:35:06,787
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The moment of truth has come.</font>

397
00:35:06,787 --> 00:35:07,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

398
00:35:07,657 --> 00:35:12,097
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Undefeated street racer
 Takahashi Ryosuke of the Akagi Red Suns...</font>

399
00:35:12,097 --> 00:35:17,307
