412
00:36:46,787 --> 00:36:49,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's your prediction as well, Shingo ?</font>

413
00:36:50,427 --> 00:36:52,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Just like you, I'd say.</font>

414
00:36:53,447 --> 00:36:54,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You too.</font>

415
00:37:03,627 --> 00:37:06,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takumi isn't here yet.</font>

