418
00:37:14,537 --> 00:37:20,347
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Iketani, what brings so many people here ?</font>

419
00:37:21,217 --> 00:37:25,027
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Well, it could be a yearning.</font>

420
00:37:25,987 --> 00:37:27,087
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">A yearning...?</font>

421
00:37:27,727 --> 00:37:32,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">A yearning for the super technique demonstrated by Takahashi Ryosuke and Takumi.</font>

422
00:37:33,177 --> 00:37:38,667
