423
00:37:55,787 --> 00:37:57,847
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Here comes the panda Trueno !</font>

424
00:37:57,847 --> 00:38:00,377
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's Akina's downhill specialist, huh ?</font>

425
00:38:00,377 --> 00:38:04,667
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Once you see his splendid drift,
