426
00:38:12,547 --> 00:38:15,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Finally, the crowd's pumped up, Sayuki.</font>

427
00:38:16,307 --> 00:38:18,127
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He's good.</font>

