436
00:38:51,907 --> 00:38:56,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We need you when the stakes are high.</font>

437
00:38:58,787 --> 00:39:04,937
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Only two drivers have made 
me feel that I'll eventually lose.</font>

438
00:39:05,847 --> 00:39:08,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">One of them is you, Keisuke.</font>

439
00:39:09,507 --> 00:39:10,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Me ?</font>

440
00:39:11,527 --> 00:39:13,537
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">And the other one...</font>

441
00:39:33,607 --> 00:39:38,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Don't worry. 
I don't think I'll lose any time soon.</font>

442
00:39:44,007 --> 00:39:44,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takumi !</font>

443
00:39:45,647 --> 00:39:48,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Tonight, I'll drive at full throttle.</font>

444
00:39:49,657 --> 00:39:51,757
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It'll be fun.</font>

445
00:40:24,367 --> 00:40:25,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm going to count down !</font>

446
00:40:31,387 --> 00:40:32,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">In five...</font>

447
00:40:32,657 --> 00:40:33,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Four...</font>

448
00:40:33,507 --> 00:40:34,367
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Three...</font>

449
00:40:34,667 --> 00:40:35,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Two...</font>

450
00:40:35,557 --> 00:40:36,647
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">One...</font>

451
00:40:36,647 --> 00:40:37,667
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Go !</font>

452
00:40:39,867 --> 00:40:45,647
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's begun ! It's the best downhill battle 
