<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">My brother's standard 
strategy in an important battle.</font></font>

456
00:40:56,757 --> 00:40:59,767
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">{wazato}He deliberately lets his opponent take the lead, and then overtakes them.</font></font>

457
00:40:59,767 --> 00:41:02,227
