484
00:44:15,047 --> 00:44:16,577
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">{osoroshii}He's frighteningly good.</font></font>

485
00:44:19,697 --> 00:44:21,727
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">It's no good, I can't shake him !</font></font>

